<li id="cite_note-2"><b><a href="#cite_ref-2" title="">^</a></b> <a href="/wiki/Star_Trek" title="Star Trek">Star Trek</a> has an extremely large following but can still be considered 'cult' due to the intense loyalty the franchise inspires; see <a href="/wiki/Cult_following" title="Cult following">Cult following</a></li>
